    "title": "Flipkart Logistics is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Senior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Flipkart Logistics! We are hiring a Warehouse Manager for our Bhopal team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Flipkart Logistics:\nFlipkart Logistics is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Flipkart Logistics!",
